{"tid":1487745,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[影] 台灣總統蔡英文談香港 觀眾批中國豪洨","createTime":"2019-08-19T11:39:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T11:39:35.000Z","uid":296328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9a1f86e6b937c8e9b67bc4eb6f128a954a8a74fa","tid":1487745,"uid":296328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:39:35.000Z","msg":"前幾日，台灣總統<span style=\"color: green;\">蔡英文</span>在台中演講，席間談到香港近日情況。<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">蔡英文</span>說，她近來對香港的支持，被<span style=\"color: blue;\">中國國民黨</span>以消費港人處境的地獄梗「撿到槍」來形容，<span style=\"color: green;\">蔡英文</span>也表示不能接受與無奈。<br />\n另一方面，在總結<span style=\"color: red;\">一國兩制</span>時，台下觀眾接著回答，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一國兩制</span>是「豪洨」(台語指&quot;謊言&quot;、&quot;詐騙&quot;之意) ，<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">蔡英文</span>則幽默稱自己年輕時被父親聽到自己說「賭爛」(台語&quot;不爽&quot;、&quot;生氣&quot;之意) 的情境來回應觀眾。<br />\n影片連結:<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2ZcciMy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZcciMy&d=00b%2B5OzPsUCZ7nX0ilF464OqxcwteoRdaW8BGlJRIvY%3D&h=b9bac4bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2ZcciMy</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gq9btnc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgq9btnc.jpg&h=6f93cfd0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}